# Package Manager

- Use Bun for dependency and script commands in this project.
- Prefer `bun install` for dependency installation and lockfile updates.
- Prefer `bun add <package>` and `bun remove <package>` when changing dependencies.
- Prefer `bun run <script>` for package scripts, such as `bun run lint` or `bun run build`.
- Keep `bun.lock` as the package manager lockfile. Do not introduce `package-lock.json`, `yarn.lock`, or `pnpm-lock.yaml`.
